profile:
At Hometurf Lawn Care, we have been treating the lawns of our loyal customers for over 30 years. As a family-owned and -operated business, we have grown by delivering lush, healthy, green lawns while using only the highest quality products applied by professional lawn care technicians. Let us help you make your lawn look its best this season!

Our season-long lawn care programs take the guess work out of which products to use and when. Applications are scheduled to be applied four to six weeks apart throughout the season for optimal turf care. We strive to ensure everything your lawn needs is included in our programs. No telemarketing or sales calls pushing unnecessary extras.

Our services include: lawn care programs, lawn maintenance programs, fertilizer, weed control, insect control, aeration, grass seeding, dethatching, top dressing, chinch bug control and grub control.

profile:
TERRA CARE LANDSCAPING AND PROPERTY MANAGEMENT LTD IS A FAMILY-OWNED, FULL SERVICE LAWN AND LANDSCAPING BUSINESS  THAT HAS BEEN SERVING BOTH COMMERCIAL AND RESIDENTIAL CLIENTS THROUGHOUT THE GTA . SINCE OUR FOUNDING, TERRA CARE HAS CONTINUOUSLY SEEN GROWTH AND EXPANSION. UNLIKE OTHER LANDSCAPING COMPANIES,  OUR FOUNDATION OF PUTTING THE CUSTOMER FIRST AND TREATING YOUR PROPERTY AS IF IT WERE OUR OWN HAS ONLY INTENSIFIED AS WE'VE CONTINUED TO GROW.
OUR HIGHEST QUALITY  SERVICES, CUSTOMER SERVICE  AND COMPETITIVE PRICES HAVE DEVELOPED US INTO TORONTO'S PREMIERE CHOICE FOR LAWN CARE AND LANDSCAPING SERVICES.
WE PROMISE TO DO WHATEVER IT TAKES TO MAKE OUR CLIENTS MORE THAN SATISFIED WITH OUR WORK AND GET EVERY LANDSCAPING JOB DONE PROPERLY. OUR CLIENTS FEEL LIKE FAMILY BECAUSE LANDSCAPING IS BEYOND PLANTS, TREES AND SOD. IT IS A LIVING EXAMPLE OF OUR ONTARIO LIFESTYLE AND CULTURE. OUR CREWS HAVE EXPERTISE, SKILLS AND TOOLS TO HELP MAINTAIN YOUR LANDSCAPING NEEDS AND HAVING IT LOOK LIKE A PERSONAL SLICE OF HEAVEN.
